# Technical stack

- **Engine:** Godot 4.x (this repo targets **4.6**; see `project.godot` `config/features`).
- **Language:** GDScript 2.
- **Template / addons:** `addons/maaacks_game_template/`, `addons/ggt-core/`, `addons/ggt-debug-shortcuts/` (enabled plugins and autoloads such as `SceneLoader`, `GGT`, `AppConfig`, audio/UI controllers per `project.godot`).
- **Project code:** `scenes/`, `scripts/` — prefer new behavior and forks of template flows here rather than editing addon sources unless fixing a bug or updating the template intentionally.
- **Testing:** No bundled unit-test addon; use focused test scenes/scripts under `res://tests/` or adopt **GdUnit4** / **GUT** if you add one (see `.cursor/agents/test-writer.md`).
